data.description: The Sacramento River is just moments away from this Charming 4-bedroom,2-bath home nestled in the picturesque Lake California Subdivision. Revel in the comfort of a brand-new roof and exquisite vinyl flooring that seamlessly blends style and durability. Vaulted ceilings, spacious living room, wood stove, ceiling fans throughout, large En' Suite Primary bedroom with walk in closet and slider door to the back patio and attached 2 car Garage. This residence offers not just a home but a lifestyle, complete with a private Community Lake, Sacramento River boat ramp area, equestrian center, Campground, playground, Airstrip, Community center and more... Unlock the door to your dream home today.
